\begin_layout Standard
This method is designed to highlight regions where ice features based on
 SIC estimates are more variable between the years.
 The NOAA/NSIDC CDR climatological 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{\sigma}_{SIA}^{n}$
\end_inset

 is shown in Fig.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:Climatological-median"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

